nk'><img alt="BB战士武者编年史——武者列传（一）" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202009/11/5f5acce29fd306930.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">嘴部没有雪铁龙式样的散热口，看细节像Z高达<br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k4z7w7/pic_57/' target='_blank'><img alt="BB战士武者编年史——武者列传（一）" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202009/11/5f5acce2a6dad548.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k4z7w7/pic_58/' target='_blank'><img alt="BB战士武者编年史——武者列传（一）" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202009/11/5f5acce31a1d85164.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k4z7w7/pic_59/' target='_blank'><img alt="BB战士武者编年史——武者列传（一）" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202009/11/5f5acce31fe0c361.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k4z7w7/pic_60/' target='_blank'><img alt="BB战士武者编年史——武者列传（一）" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202009/11/5f5acce31af2c1336.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k4z7w7/pic_61/' target='_blank'><img alt="BB战士武者编年史——武者列传（一）" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202009/11/5f5acce35fda97714.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k4z7w7/pic_62/' target='_blank'><img alt="BB战士武者编年史——武者列传（一）" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202009/11/5f5acce3775f24603.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k4z7w7/pic_63/' target='_blank'><img alt="BB战士武者编年史——武者列传（一）" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202009/11/5f5acce377f482135.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k4z7w7/pic_64/' target='_blank'><img alt="BB战士武者编年史——武者列传（一）" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202009/11/5f5acce3c963c630.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/a5k4z7w7/pic_65/' target='_blank'><img alt="BB战士武者编年史——武者列传（一）" src="