</div></div><p itemprop="description">g304图片观感极佳，但是上“眼”之后跟英菲克似的。</p><span class="embed-card  main-site res_smzdm" style=""><a target="_blank" onclick="dataLayer.push({'event':'1200041','pagetitle':'电脑数码 篇一：罗技g304与g300s的对比和使用感受'});" class=" res_smzdm" href="https://wiki.smzdm.com/" ><span class="z-tag-baike res_smzdm">百科</span></a><span class="embed-card-logo res_smzdm"><a target="_blank" onclick="dataLayer.push({'event':'1200041','pagetitle':'电脑数码 篇一：罗技g304与g300s的对比和使用感受'});" class=" res_smzdm" href="https://wiki.smzdm.com/p/8w1ryr4/" ><img ol  alt="罗技g304与g300s的对比和使用感受" class="res_smzdm" src="https://qny.smzdm.com/201808/17/5b766c39580ff2258.jpg_a200.jpg" ></a></span><span class="embed-card-info res_smzdm"><a target="_blank" onclick="dataLayer.push({'event':'1200041','pagetitle':'电脑数码 篇一：罗技g304与g300s的对比和使用感受'});" class=" res_smzdm" href="https://wiki.smzdm.com/p/8w1ryr4/" ><span class="card-name res_smzdm">inphic 英菲克 PM6 无线鼠标</span></a><span class="card-abstract res_smzdm">英菲克PM6无线鼠标采用磨砂表面，三档DPI可调，最高1600DPI，2.4G无线连接，无线频率为2402-2480MHz，传输距离约为10米，共有6个快速响应按键，鼠标尺寸为120*78*38mm，约重95g。</span><span class="card-controls res_smzdm"><span class="group-data res_smzdm"> <i>值</i>0</span><span class="group-data res_smzdm"> <i>点评</i>1</span><span class="group-data res_smzdm"> <i>原创</i>9</span><span class="group-data res_smzdm"> <i>好价</i>0</span><a target="_blank" onclick="gtmAddToCart({'name':'inphic 英菲克 PM6 无线鼠标','id':'a07o8wqz' ,'dimension16':'','dimension19':'', 'price':'无','brand':'无' ,'mall':'无', 'category':'无/无/无/无','metric1':'无','dimension10':'smzdm.com','dimension9':'yuanchuang','dimension11':'无','dimension20':'无','dimension25':'无','dimension64':'yuanchuang'});if(typeof change_direct_url != 'undefined' && change_direct_url instanceof Function){change_direct_url(this)}" class=" res_smzdm" href="https://go.smzdm.com/2821ce1cc377c785/ca_bb_yc_163_70636885_10869_1773_183_0"  rel="nofollow" ><span class="card-btn-deep res_smzdm">去购买</span></a><a target="_blank" onclick="dataLaye